{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"labelsVisibility"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"visibility"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Visibility","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore10VisibilityO","text":"Visibility"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier when you want to omit a label from one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"labeled content in your user interface. For example, the first "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Toggle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the following example hides its label:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["VStack {","    Toggle(isOn: $toggle1) {","        Text(\"Toggle 1\")","    }","    .labelsVisibility(.hidden)","","    Toggle(isOn: $toggle2) {","        Text(\"Toggle 2\")","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" in the example above centers the first toggle’s control"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"element in the available space, while it centers the second toggle’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"combined label and control element:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Always provide a label for controls, even when you hide the label,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"because OpenSwiftUI uses labels for other purposes, including accessibility.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"On iOS, a ","type":"text"},{"code":"Picker","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" within a ","type":"text"},{"code":"Menu","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" hides its label by default. You can use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this modifier to explicitly show the label in that context:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["Menu {","    Picker(\"Flavor\", selection: $selectedFlavor) {","        Text(\"Chocolate\").tag(Flavor.chocolate)","        Text(\"Vanilla\").tag(Flavor.vanilla)","        Text(\"Strawberry\").tag(Flavor.strawberry)","    }","    .labelsVisibility(.visible)","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This modifier doesn’t work for all labels. It applies to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/LabeledContent","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" elements, including controls like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Picker"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Toggle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":", but not to controls like a bordered button where the label","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is inside the button’s border.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/color\/labelsvisibility(_:)"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Controls the visibility of labels of any controls contained within this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color\/labelsVisibility(_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP0aB2UIE16labelsVisibilityyQrAA0G0OF::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore5ColorV","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"labelsVisibility","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore10VisibilityO","text":"Visibility","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"labelsVisibility(_:)","platforms":[{"beta":false,"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"beta":false,"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"10.15","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"beta":false,"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"beta":false,"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"beta":false,"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false}],"symbolKind":"method","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUI\/View\/LabelContent\/LabelVisibility.swift#L60","fileName":"LabelVisibility.swift"}},"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/doc